446
00:30:15,910 --> 00:30:18,990
Kacang kenari, jujube,
kismis, buah goji.

447
00:30:19,030 --> 00:30:20,020
Masukkan semuanya.

448
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:22,230
Bergeraklah lebih cepat.

449
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:27,520
Tuan Putri.

450
00:30:29,550 --> 00:30:30,680
Cicipi ini.

451
